title: Group Therapy: Her Daughter is OBSESSED with Her New Boyfriend
description: Kathy has a 14 year old daughter who recently started dating a boy that she goes to school with and she's obsessed with him.  They're constantly on the phone and she even snuck out to see him recently. Kathy wants to know if she should do anything about it or just let it fizzle out.
